title: Corps welcomes Class of 1965 and Highty-Tighty alumni for Homecoming (Virginia Tech - Virginia Polytechnic ...
text: ( Source : Virginia Tech - Virginia Polytechnic Institute and State University ) BLACKSBURG, Va., Oct. 15, 2015 - The Virginia Tech Corps of Cadets will welcome the Class of 1965 back to campus to celebrate their entrance into the Old Guard.
